{"tid":2425229,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孟達死左，邊個最開心","createTime":"2021-02-27T08:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T09:03:17.000Z","uid":18012,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6c7b69deca474e3655ab9c1962f76bb89ccdfb6b","tid":2425229,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"原來孟達曾降魏<br />\n所以有蜀孟達, 魏孟達, 但係冇吳孟達<br />\n<br />\n劉備入蜀時，劉璋派遣孟達和法正去迎接劉備，劉備命其駐守江陵，蜀平後為宜都太守。建安二十四年（219年），孟達從秭歸北攻房陵，殺死房陵太守蒯祺，（諸葛亮的姐夫）攻下房陵後繼續進攻上庸，並和劉封會合於此地。關羽圍樊城、襄陽時（樊城之戰），曾要求劉封和孟達派兵援助，但被劉封和孟達拒絕，關羽戰敗後，孟達因畏懼被治罪，再加上跟劉封不和，於是帶著部下郤揖投降曹魏[1]。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/孟達\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AD%9F%E9%81%94&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=dcfbc4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/孟達</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n孟達之亂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新城之亂是三國時期227年年末[1]至228年初[2]曹魏的一場叛亂。叛亂發起者為投魏及受任為荊州新城郡守的原蜀將孟達。此亂在一月之內即被魏將司馬懿迅速平定，孟達被俘伏誅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/孟達\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E5%AD%9F%E9%81%94&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEmxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=dcfbc4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/孟達</a>"},{"pid":"378382a9ae655a645d2a3cc6da9587b98a2c44ca","tid":2425229,"uid":1149,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:12:53.000Z","msg":"石頭佬死連登仔最開心"},{"pid":"c0e835c3643225d2c345b594c64006a212e81d48","tid":2425229,"uid":58209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"孟母$3000"},{"pid":"631a71d8fe3a8c7b7b7b05bfbd80142528419026","tid":2425229,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T08:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src